Squee : you misunderstood, I am saying that the song of rest sucks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   However, bard and minstrel healing song are the same than bards, so I think all three songs should be improved. I'll say it again, i don't want something uber powerful, I want a point in using those songs at all (at 50 in a group, I know this song is mildly useful at level 15 solo).<br>
<br>
As I pointed out in my &quot;rantish&quot; thread, I do agree with the melee vs shouts tradeoff, and I think it is fine that our shouts and song have an endurance usage.<br>
However, compared to other classes with similar abilities, it appears that all skald's and minstrel's shouts are grossly overpriced (compared to bards, champions, thanes ...). The price to pay in power and endurance should be brought down accordingly. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ufubbor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fubbor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Member</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#ff0000>(10/7/02 5:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=347.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Here it is - WIP Skald Report</span><hr size=1> Well I havent played my skald in mounths and I see we are still asking for all the same stuff.  Has Myth done anything good for Skalds latly??? <p>Icebane
  
