Face it, most of the complaints about skalds beeing overpowered do NOT come from other realms. You will never, ever see a champion or friar dare to say skalds are overpowered. You can just look at the boards, 75% of the crowd that consider us overpowered are the mids, especially thanes and warriors.<br>
It just looks like we are what thanes dream to be, they seem to see us as the prime exemple of what a melee hybrid should be and the bitter proof that their class is gimped.<br>
<br>
On paper, imho, thanes with similar level, equipment and RA will own us on duels.<br>
They have the same hp and damage table.<br>
They have comparable stats (pie instead of cha), depending on race, plus a 50 str bonus<br>
They have a superior damage add.<br>
They have superior combat skills - 2.0 instead of 1.5, similar investment between stormcalling and battlesongs<br>
They have speccable shield, including access to stun styles<br>
They have a slightly lower (but less costly, even factoring the PBAE shout cost) &quot;insta DD&quot; dps, but not by a large margin (you can find the numbers in my monster rant thread).<br>
They have 1500 range castable DD on top of the instas<br>
<br>
Kiting and &quot;DD DD style mez&quot; will not work well if the thane is fully prepared and play well. They can frontload damage almost as well as skalds,  have the same timers on their instas, and have actually more range and comparable DD ability, so the snaring tactics won't work either.<br>
<br>
Well I am not saying this to imply thanes are not gimped or that skalds are weaker than thanes, especially considering the whole RvR situation which do not consist in 1vs1 duels. <br>
However, I do think that a bit of dueling will give to people who consider us as &quot;warriors with speed and mez&quot; a little reality check. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showMessageRange?topicID=347.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=347.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=347.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=347.topic&index=24><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=347.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.threadControl?topicID=347.topic><img src=http://www.stuckathome.com/skalded/images/closethread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=347.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=347.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td alig